import React, { Component } from 'react'
import {Navbar,Nav,NavItem} from 'react-bootstrap';
import {Link } from 'react-router-dom';

export default class CustomNavbar extends Component {
    render() {
        return (
            <Navbar default collapseOnSelect>
                <Navbar.Header>
                    <Navbar.Brand>
                        <Link to="/">Sereal Koding</Link>
                    </Navbar.Brand>
                    <Navbar.Toggle/>
                </Navbar.Header>
                <Navbar.Collapse>
                    <Nav pullRight>
                        <NavItem eventKeys={1} componentClass={Link}  to="/">
                            Home
                        </NavItem>
                        <NavItem eventKeys={1} componentClass={Link}  to="/about">
                            About
                        </NavItem>
                        <NavItem eventKeys={1} componentClass={Link}  to="/news">
                            News
                        </NavItem>
                    </Nav>
                </Navbar.Collapse>
            </Navbar>
        )
    }
}
